Name: CustomerNotExist
Description: Indicates that the customer does not exist (email or username)

Name: WrongPassword
Description: Indicates that the provided password is incorrect

Name: NotActive
Description: Indicates that the account has not been activated

Name: Deleted
Description: Indicates that the customer account has been deleted

Name: NotRegistered
Description: Indicates that the customer is not registered

Name: LockedOut
Description: Indicates that the customer account is locked out

Name: MultiFactorAuthenticationRequired
Description: Indicates that multi-factor authentication is required
